%% Diagram: Custom Element Lifecycle
%% Type: state
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
stateDiagram-v2
  direction TB
  [*] --> Constructed: new or upgrade
  Constructed --> Connected: connectedCallback
  Connected --> AttributeChanged: attributeChangedCallback
  AttributeChanged --> Connected: sync or render
  Connected --> Adopted: adoptedCallback
  Adopted --> Connected: still connected
  Connected --> Connected: connectedMoveCallback (moveBefore)
  Connected --> Disconnected: disconnectedCallback
  Disconnected --> Connected: re-inserted
  Disconnected --> [*]: GC when unreachable
